features: TV AERIAL CONNECTOR: Connect your television, radio, and other satellite receiving devices to each other with our satellite cable connectors by Keple. This F connector to coax adaptor features and IEC coax female socket to a type F plug.

STABLE TRANSMISSION: The nickel-plated brass provides a strong and stable transmission to prevent signal loss between your devices. Our F connector to TV aerial connector also features a high transfer speed for RF antenna devices.
MALE-TO-FEMALE DESIGN: These sky cable connectors are resistant to corrosion and oxidation. This adapter plugs into a type F socket and provides a way to connect your devices with TV Aerial plugs.

VERSATILE APPLICATIONS: The IEC coax plug is one of the oldest coaxial connectors still used in consumer electronics today, though many TVs and RF devices use F connectors. This Aerial adaptor has versatile uses when connecting new and old devices.

EASY INSTALLATION: This TV aerial connector screws into your devices for quick and simple installation. We recommend checking your devices to make sure that these coaxial cable connectors are correct for your needs.
description: Keple F Connector to Coax Connector (IEC) Are you looking for an easy way to link your IEC coax device to an F-type television or radio? Look no further as Keple offers a quality TV aerial connector to suit your needs. This F-type male to IEC coax female connector is crafted from nickel-plated brass for a stable transmission. Our coaxial cable connectors provide a high-speed transfer between your linked devices. Simply screw this F connector into your TV, radio, or other RF appliances to have a convenient Aeriel socket at your fingertips. Please check the device you plan to use before purchasing these satellite cable connectors. At Keple, we offer a large assortment of adapters to make your life easier. Our goal is to provide you with same quality connectors that help technicians and engineers simplify their jobs. Our adaptors require no special tools to install. Key Features Adapter Type: IEC Coax Female to F-Type Male Body Style: Straight Impedance: 75 Ohm Amount: 2 Pack
